question: Please provide me the payer that paid for the medication amLODIPine 2.5 MG Oral Tablet.

             JOIN claims c ON p.id = c.primarypatientinsuranceid

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.id) 
             FROM patients p 
             LEFT JOIN allergies a ON p.id=a.patient 
             WHERE a.code IN (SELECT code FROM allergies WHERE description='Eggs (edible) (substance)'); 

            [Q]: 'Can you provide the count of patients suffering from Eggs (edible) (substance) and have a claim with the ID 2bfc5ac8-bf25-4845-f673-c6f6bc344034?'
            [SQL]: 
             SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.id) 
             FROM patients p 
             LEFT JOIN allergies a ON p.id=a.patient 
             LEFT JOIN claims c ON p.id=c.patientid 
             WHERE a.code IN (SELECT code FROM allergies WHERE description='Eggs (edible) (substance)') 
             AND c.id='2bfc5ac8-bf25-4845-f673-c6f6bc344034

question: In which encounter was a procedure with code 710824005 performed?

             FROM procedures p
             JOIN encounters e ON p.encounter = e.id

             ORDER BY p.base_cost DESC
             LIMIT 1;

             JOIN patients pa ON e.patient = pa.id
             JOIN allergies a ON pa.id = a.patient AND a.code = 'Allergy to substance (finding)'
             ORDER BY m.base_cost DESC
             LIMIT
